{"type":"answer","id":238446,"parentType":"question","parentId":7333,"uid":33968,"contents":"沒漲。台灣政府都有公佈統計數據。<br>\n依政府公佈的數據，台灣普通受薪階層年給大約450萬台幣(10W RMB)。<br>\n(https://earnings.dgbas.gov.tw/)<br>\n<br>\n薪資：<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/Ku4TLr2.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/Ku4TLr2.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/Ku4TLr2.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n(https://www.thenewslens.com/article/110996)<br>\n<br>\n物價：<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/h1E3Im1.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/h1E3Im1.png\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/h1E3Im1.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n(https://www.masterhsiao.com.tw/Smart/SC194/SC194.php)<br>\n<br>\n=====<br>\n台灣是已開發國家。科技進步使社會生產力增長，薪資纔會長。近廿年，生產方式沒有變化，薪資也自然沒有變化。","date":"2020-04-13","agreeCount":1,"discussionCount":0}